The evidence with the title 'So, does card check kill the secret ballot or not? ' says Mar 10, 2009  ... Maybe that 's why debate over the EFCA hangs on a single, simple question: does the measure eliminate the " secret ballot" in union elections? Business groups like the U.S. Chamber Of Commerce say yes . (Warren Buffett has voiced his concern as well . )Labor groups like the SEIU and AFL-CIO say no. 
